(intake:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Federal and non-federal parcel exchange, including lands entering and leaving National Forest) Tj T*
(System ownership.) Tj T*
(- Road and trail easements, Sweet Trunk Trail No. 274 construction, Inspiration Divide Trail No. 8) Tj T*
(relocation, and Big Timber Canyon Trailhead improvement.) Tj T*
(- Wetland, riparian, and monitoring-access deed restrictions.) Tj T*
(- Grazing allotment, permit, fence, road, irrigation ditch, and related improvement changes.) Tj T*
(- Hazardous-materials and site-condition due diligence before conveyance.) Tj T*
(- Climate, carbon, vegetation, and restoration context where those topics depend on soil condition,) Tj T*
(productivity, or revegetation assumptions.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Required Tasks) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Confirm the soils analysis boundary.) Tj T*
