(areas, access easements, improvement areas, wetlands/riparian buffers, and any construction or) Tj T*
(restoration footprints.) Tj T*
(  - State whether soils analysis is limited to disturbance and restoration areas or also includes) Tj T*
(broader parcel management consequences after ownership transfer.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. Compile baseline soils information.) Tj T*
(  - Collect available soil survey, ecological site, slope, erosion-hazard, mass-movement,) Tj T*
(hydrologic soil group, road/trail, wetland/riparian, vegetation, and invasive-species data.) Tj T*
